# Phase 4 Theme Global Foundation Boundary

During Phase 4, theme work is limited to **global layout shell and presentation scaffolding**.

## Allowed

- Header, footer, nav, mobile drawer, cart link shell
- CSS tokens, layout grid, focus states, reduced-motion defaults
- Theme helpers (`resq_theme_*`) with plugin guards
- Empty-safe template parts that consume plugin helpers
- Planning-route nav links from docs/07

## Prohibited

- Product/taxonomy/CPT registration or meta writes
- Woo template overrides beyond empty-safe template parts (Phase 5)
- Gateway page content (Phase 6)
- Cart drawer behavior, bundle engine, checkout mutations
- Hard-coded product catalog truth or risky claims

